---
source: src/core/situation.rs
assertion: situation commands classify tasks and plan links with heuristic signals
schema:
  classify: ee.situation.classify.v1
  compare: ee.situation.compare.v1
  link_dry_run: ee.situation.link_dry_run.v1
  show: ee.situation.show.v1
  explain: ee.situation.explain.v1
contracts:
  - classify returns category with confidence based on keyword signals
  - density-aware lift caps confidence at 0.49 for single signal
  - multi-signal tasks can reach confidence >= 0.7
  - compare dry-run returns relation and overlap score
  - link dry-run plans curation candidate without persisting
  - show returns not-found for unknown situation IDs (no persistence yet)
  - explain returns not-found for unknown situation IDs (no persistence yet)
evidence:
  - ClassifyResult.category
  - ClassifyResult.confidence
  - ClassifyResult.signals
  - SituationCompareReport.relation
  - SituationLinkDryRunReport.curation_candidate
